# ctm316 Color System: Technical Report

## 1. Executive Summary
The **ctm316** project is a high-precision color design monorepo comprising a standalone Web Application and a Figma Plugin. It leverages advanced color math and perceptual luminance targeting to generate balanced color ramps and semantic design tokens that adhere to WCAG 2.1 accessibility standards.

---

## 2. Web Application: Feature Audit
The Web Application serves as the primary designer interface and documentation engine.

### Core Features
| Feature | Status | Description | Component |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Perceptual Ramp Generation** | ✅ | Generates ramps based on target luminance rather than linear HSL steps. | `ClrGen.js` |
| **Multi-Method Creation** | ✅ | Supports **Balanced** (perceptual), **Linear** (standard), and **Symmetric** modes. | `ClrGen.js` |
| **Contrast-Based Mapping** | ✅ | Automatically selects base colors that meet specific WCAG contrast targets. | `ClrGen.js` |
| **Manual Override Mapping** | ✅ | Allows designers to specify a manual base index for role tokens. | `ClrGen.js` |
| **Live UI Generation** | ✅ | Real-time preview of ramps and theme tokens with interactive controls. | `UiGen.js` |
| **Documentation Exports** | ✅ | Export system as **CSS Variables**, **SCSS Maps**, or **CSV** documentation. | `DocGen.js` |
| **Config Persistence** | ✅ | JSON-based import/export for sharing and saving design system states. | `UiGen.js` |
| **Accessibility Audit** | ✅ | Integrated WCAG 2.1 contrast ratio and rating display (AA/AAA) for all steps. | `Utils.js` |

---

## 3. Figma Plugin: Feature Audit
The Figma Plugin synchronizes the design system directly with Figma's native Variable engine.

### Core Features
| Feature | Status | Description | Component |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Variable Sync Engine** | ✅ | Bi-directional sync of color groups and semantic roles to Figma. | `scripts.js` |
| **Contextual Aliasing** | ✅ | Maps semantic tokens to raw variables using Figma Variable Aliases. | `scripts.js` |
| **Thematic Modes** | ✅ | Automatically maps Light and Dark themes to Figma Variable Modes. | `scripts.js` |
| **In-Plugin Preview** | ✅ | High-fidelity preview of all generated tokens without leaving the canvas. | `ui.html` |
| **Granular Updates** | ✅ | Choice to update all variables, only raw groups, or only semantic roles. | `ui.html` |
| **Contrast Awareness** | ✅ | Visual warnings and automatic adjustments for non-compliant tokens. | `scripts.js` |
| **Resizable Interface** | ✅ | Premium UI with custom resize handles and TailwindCSS integration. | `ui.html` |

